data.description: Priced to Sell! Immerse yourself in this exquisite two-story residence featuring 4 bedrooms, a den, and an additional bonus room ideal for a children's play area or home theater. The main floor encompasses a versatile space suitable for a den, office, or formal dining, adorned with herringbone tile and double glass doors. The open floor plan seamlessly flows into a spacious kitchen and dining area. Upstairs, you'll find 4 bedrooms, each boasting walk-in closets, along with 3 full baths and the bonus room. The master bedroom boasts a private deck with captivating mountain views. Nestled against an expansive open space, this home offers a private play pool and a secluded corner fire pit area.
